This paper involves natural language processing techniques to identify sensitive topics on a Chinese microblogging site. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Computation and Language (cs.CL), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), and Sound (cs.SD) which deal with topics related to social media analysis, natural language processing, cybersecurity, and security.
